        <article class="markdown-body entry-content" itemprop="text"><h1><a id="user-content-blended---a-scala-based-integration-framework" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#blended---a-scala-based-integration-framework"><svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>Blended - a Scala based Integration framework</h1>
<div id="user-content-preamble">
<div>
<div>
<p><span><a href="https://circleci.com/gh/woq-blended/blended" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/3015d1c55b7748bd8dfbfd52e96b87d697546ad4/68747470733a2f2f636972636c6563692e636f6d2f67682f776f712d626c656e6465642f626c656e6465642e7376673f7374796c653d737667" alt="CircleCI" data-canonical-src="https://circleci.com/gh/woq-blended/blended.svg?style=svg" style="max-width:100%;"></a></span>
